<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="External_links">External links</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Bobbio_Abbey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14" title="Edit section: External links"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
<ul><li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.comune.bobbio.pc.it/sottolivello.asp?idsa=9&amp;idam=&amp;idbox=20&amp;idvocebox=166">Bobbio Municipal website:history</a>  <span class="languageicon">(in Italian)</span></li>
<li><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20101223101751/http://video.libero.it/app/play?id=7d3ddafe6503cbeeed3cd0c5f6a7c543">Abbey's video</a></li></ul>
